# 08: The AdamW Optimizer

```elixir
Code.require_file("setup.exs", __DIR__)

Mix.install(
  [
    {:nx, "~> 0.10"},
    {:exla, "~> 0.10"},
    {:kino, "~> 0.14"},
    {:vega_lite, "~> 0.1"},
    {:kino_vega_lite, "~> 0.1"}
  ] ++ NotebookSetup.platform_deps()
